scenes.description: Amelia Watson, Takanashi Kiara, and Ninomae Ina'nis conclude their performance of "Digital Girl".
Transition to the next song performance, with on-screen text identifying the upcoming track.
Takanashi Kiara performs a solo rendition of "The Bigaku" by Matsuura Aya.
